eu.trentorise.opendata.jackan.model

Class CkanDatasetBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.trentorise.opendata.jackan.model.CkanDatasetBase
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CkanDataset

    public class CkanDatasetBase
extends Object
    A Ckan Dataset, which in turn holds Ckan Resources. In Ckan terminology it is also known as 'package'. CkanDatasetBase holds fields that can be sent when creating a dataset,, while CkanDataset holds more fields that can be returned with searches. This class initializes nothing to fully preserve all we get from ckan. In practice, all fields of retrieved resources can be null except maybe name.
    Since:
    0.4.1
    Author:
    David Leoni
